247
00:23:39,104 --> 00:23:41,310
- Mm-hm.
- OK.

248
00:23:41,815 --> 00:23:43,891
Is that it?

249
00:23:44,609 --> 00:23:46,685
All right.

250
00:23:57,331 --> 00:23:59,407
Hey, what's the what?

251
00:23:59,500 --> 00:24:02,454
