948
01:35:39,544 --> 01:35:41,786
<i> You saw what I did to Omar?</i>

949
01:35:43,631 --> 01:35:45,707
<i>Guess who's next.</i>

950
01:35:46,634 --> 01:35:48,212
So what?

951
01:35:48,303 --> 01:35:50,876
